    <item>
      <title>法律委员会表示，英国养老金在投资时可能会考虑气候变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/uk-law-committee-says-pensions-may-consider-esg-when-investing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国金融法市场咨询委员会表示，养老金受托人在做出投资决策时可能会考虑气候变化，从而缓解了长期以来对纳入关键 ESG 因素可能违反信托义务的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/uk-law-committee-says-pensions-may-consider-esg-when-investing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞安航空赢得欧盟法院对荷航 Covid-19 援助批准的上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ryanair-wins-eu-court-appeal-over-klm-s-covid-19-aid-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞安航空控股公司 (Ryanair Holdings Plc) 赢得了欧盟法院针对欧盟批准向竞争对手法航荷航提供 34 亿欧元（合 37 亿美元）国家援助的挑战，这是这家爱尔兰航空公司针对新冠疫情期间发放的涉嫌不公平补贴的最新一轮行动。 19 流行病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ryanair-wins-eu-court-appeal-over-klm-s-covid-19-aid-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度正在考虑延长蒸谷米税，以免影响世界供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/india-mulls-extending-parboiled-rice-tax-in-risk-to-world-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为全球最大的大米出口国，印度可能会延长预煮品种的出口税，作为全国选举前缓解食品通胀努力的一部分，此举可能会导致世界供应紧张，并将价格推至新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/india-mulls-extending-parboiled-rice-tax-in-risk-to-world-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:52:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度通过具有里程碑意义的新供应协议从卡塔尔获得更便宜的液化天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/india-gets-cheaper-lng-from-qatar-in-landmark-new-supply-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔同意在与印度公司 Petronet LNG Ltd. 的长期合同中降低液化天然气价格，这是这家波斯湾生产商为大规模产量扩张锁定客户的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/india-gets-cheaper-lng-from-qatar-in-landmark-new-supply-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:47:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于担心工资和火山影响风扇价格，冰岛维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/iceland-holds-rates-as-wages-volcano-fallout-fan-price-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冰岛央行将基准利率维持在2009年以来的最高水平，以确保通胀继续下行，尽管工资谈判和火山活动的风险可能导致物价再度上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/iceland-holds-rates-as-wages-volcano-fallout-fan-price-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:40:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国正在采取一切措施拯救遭受重创的股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/everything-china-is-doing-to-rescue-its-battered-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当局试图阻止市场连续第四年暴跌，中国加大了救援力度，中国股市已从 7 万亿美元的暴跌中开始复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/everything-china-is-doing-to-rescue-its-battered-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:36:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着饮酒量的减少，嘉士伯的利润将适度增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlsberg-expects-moderate-profit-growth-as-drinkers-spend-less</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉士伯公司预计今年的营业利润将温和增长，因为一些消费者不再喝啤酒，而且该公司在营销上投入更多资金以专注于增长更快的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlsberg-expects-moderate-profit-growth-as-drinkers-spend-less</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:07:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银提供 10 亿美元的 AT1 作为其融资计划的快速启动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ubs-offers-1-billion-at1s-in-fast-start-to-year-s-funding-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 在制定未来几年增发数十亿美元风险证券的计划后一天，就发行了以美元计价的额外一级票据。]]></description>
