      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维斯塔斯表示，随着危机缓解，今年的前景正在改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维斯塔斯风力系统公司 (Vestas Wind Systems A/S) 预计，随着这家丹麦公司扭转了导致项目开发放缓的全行业危机，在 2023 年恢复盈利后，今年的盈利将有所改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/vestas-posts-improving-outlook-for-this-year-as-crisis-abates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管利润下降，Equinor仍将向投资者支付140亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/equinor-profit-retreats-on-lower-prices-for-natural-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Equinor ASA 表示，今年将按照石油巨头当前向投资者输送剩余现金的做法，支付 140 亿美元的股票回购和股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/equinor-profit-retreats-on-lower-prices-for-natural-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
